{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4d2cc5338e","title":"全力齐击欧震军开辟南进道路","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"599368c75a","index":0,"year":1947,"month":1,"day":18,"articleId":"4d2cc5338e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ec38a48741","type":"paragraph","text":"全力齐击欧震军开辟南进道路”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"4d2cc5338e"},{"id":"8a4dbe4f27","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年1月18日）陈、陈，菜、谭","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"4d2cc5338e"},{"id":"df969fc6bf","type":"paragraph","text":"毫无疑义，薛岳巴必和我军争夺陇海台枣两线，你们必须准备在这两线打几个大好灭战，开辟向南进攻的道路。目前除以一部打枣庄外，主力立即准各打欧震，以歼灭欧部八个旅为目标，务于一星期内准备完毕。待欧震进至陇海线，即举全力歼击之。此项准备工作意早完成愈好","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"4d2cc5338e"},{"id":"ad54826b93","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"4d2cc5338e"},{"id":"df760bfd4b","type":"paragraph","text":"子巧口I]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给山东野战军司令员兼政治委员陈毅、参谋长陈士和华中野战军司令员栗裕、政治委员谭震林的电报。121薛岳，当时任国民党军徐州级靖公署主任。[3]台枣，指山东台儿庄和枣庄。欧震，当时任国民党军整编第十九军军长。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"4d2cc5338e"}],"page":{"id":"110b9226ba","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"4d2cc5338e","start":371,"end":371}}}},"__N_SSG":true}